<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti valivēri viṣṇudēvaraku niṁdula 
<lb n="2"/>divākarapeddērikoḍuku pōtaya yā 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>caṁdrārka makhaṇḍava<unclear>r</unclear>ttidiviya 
<lb n="4"/>yokoṇṭiki niccina goṟiyalu 
<lb n="5"/>yēṁbadi Iddēvaraka yiṁdu 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>la kommiyaṣaḍaṁggavikoḍu 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ku savviyaṣaḍaṁgavi yācaṁdrā 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>rka makhaṇḍavarttidiviya yoko 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ṇṭiki niccina goṟiya lēṁbadi 
